# Exclude dev/build clutter from the .vsix. Everything not listed here is
# bundled. The shipped extension needs: extension.js, language-configuration,
# the grammar, icons, and node_modules (runtime deps only) — and the bundled
# server/ binary. Dev tooling, editor config, and source maps are dropped.
.vscode/**
.gitignore
**/*.map
scripts/**
**/@vscode/vsce/**
**/.DS_Store